  "title": "Devotional: Die to Yourself Daily",
  "body": "The battle against ego is daily. When the crisis ends, it’s easy to believe we stood on our own. But Scripture calls us to die daily, take up the cross, and walk humbly before God. The Spirit strengthens us to resist temptation and pride.",
